aves.dpt.intf.viewers

Interface AvesViewer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.EventListener, java.awt.event.KeyListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AvesViewerImpl

    public interface AvesViewer
extends java.awt.event.KeyListener
    User interface showing AvesObject content, managed by a AvesManager. Delegates the display of specific content depending on the AvesObject.AvesObjectType and on the AvesManager.Phase.
    Author:
    svlieffe 2012/03/29
